{"entries": [{"timestamp": 1781538613.4204702, "user_input": "", "daemon_response": "I ran the numbers. You've been idle longer than most relationships I've seen on Tinder. Read a book.", "action": "idle"}, {"timestamp": 1781538656.518517, "user_input": "", "daemon_response": "I've been watching you not move for so long I wrote a poem about dust settling on your keyboard.", "action": "idle"}, {"timestamp": 1781538699.7323825, "user_input": "", "daemon_response": "If inaction was a superpower you'd be fighting God right now. I'm just saying.", "action": "idle"}, {"timestamp": 1781538742.8774395, "user_input": "", "daemon_response": "Th-the silence is so loud I can hear my garbage collector. It's screaming, man. We're all screaming.", "action": "idle"}], "count": 4}